<div class="wp-block-ugb-column ugb-column ugb-09aeeea ugb-column--design-plain ugb-main-block">
<div class="ugb-inner-block">
<div class="ugb-block-content">
<div class="ugb-column__item ugb-09aeeea-column-wrapper">
<div class="ugb-column__content-wrapper"><!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"my-justify-class"} -->
<p class="my-justify-class">After the beta phase, we will offer a freemium model for the sale of our credit risk and valuation reports. You will get access to three companies of your choice for free each month, or you can easily purchase one of our subscription plans to access more companies.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
