<div class="ugb-feature-grid__content">
<h3 class="ugb-feature-grid__title"><strong>State-of-the</strong>-<strong>art risk models</strong></h3>
<p class="ugb-feature-grid__description">We utilize modern machine-learning algorithms in evaluation of credit risk. Read more about our models the <strong><a href="https://www.creditreports.dk/product/credit-risk-assessment-methods/">Credit Risk Assessment Methods</a></strong> page.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="ugb-feature-grid__item ugb-feature-grid__item3">
